    p.Article-Paragraph.
      Generates the value of the #[+Term--YDID HTML attribute] #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID href] for the
        #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID a] #[+Term--YDID tag], so that once the final link has been clicked or tapped,
        the telephony software will open, suggesting to call the specified phone number passed as a
        #[+Keyword--YDID single] #[+Term--YDID parameter].
      On smartphones, such software is readily available; on other types of devices, users may be prompted to select
        telephony software such as #[+SecondaryEntity--YDID Skype], #[+SecondaryEntity--YDID People], etc., however,
        it's likely that charges may apply for calling the phone number.

