    p.Article-Paragraph.
      This #[+Term--YDID function] appends #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID tel:] to the specified #[+Term--YDID string value],
        expected to be a valid phone number.
      If your code editor or #[+Term--YDID Integrated Development Environment] (#[+Term--YDID IDE]) lacks template
        autocompletion functionality, this #[+Term--YDID function] may be less convenient.
      Without autocompletion, you may need to either memorize #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID "tel:"] or the
        #[+Term--YDID function] name #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID buildPhoneNumberLinkHrefAttributeValue], or
        refer to the reference guide each time (though #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID "tel:"] consists of just three
        alphabetic letters, it might be forgotten amidst a large volume of other information).

